data.description: OPEN HOUSE CANCELED! DEADLINE SET FOR THURSDAY AT 8 PM. Lovely 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath townhome in Lohr's Orchard! At nearly 2200 finished square feet, this is the biggest model available in the community. With 3 fully finished levels that include multiple rec rooms, office spaces, and an oversized kitchen, this spacious home will meet all of your needs! The open-concept kitchen boasts a breakfast bar, sitting nook, and dining room, a wall full of windows, and a walk-out to the deck. Upstairs you'll find the primary suite with a massive walk-in closet, and large jack and jill style bathroom. Both the second and third bedrooms are generously sized as well. The expansive basement could act as a gym, additional rec room, office, or all of the above - the choice is yours! With no homes directly behind, the view here is delightful. Don't miss the fenced-in backyard and playground that's just steps away.
